Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out!\NYou can't run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up already, Abdul Hakim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So ya wanna fight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}AMIGO!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How're all you 300,000 bounty hunters{\i0}\N{\i1}in the solar system doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for BIG SHOT, the show that{\i0}\N{\i1}brings you information about fugitives!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:03:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, well, first up for today,{\i0}\N{\i1}is this guy: Abdul Hakim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's known as a serial pet thief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time, he snagged{\i0}\N{\i1}a test animal...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...from a research facility,{\i0}\N{\i1}and is on the loose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The good news is that he's{\i0}\N{\i1}worth a whopping 8 million!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The conditions are as always.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bring him in alive to{\i0}\N{\i1}collect your reward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you kill him,{\i0}\N{\i1}kiss your reward good-bye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the biggest we've had in a while.{\i0}\N{\i1}Do your best to get this guy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, why does everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor? You got information?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About Abdul Hakim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I'll take it!{\i0}\N- I'll give a discount. 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I got his post-plastic surgery picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too much. 20 down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, 280.\NOn one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sock him one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He trampled over me.{\i0}\N{\i1}If you want, punch him a dozen times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This one should be something big...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you in six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had a very conspicuous suitcase.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That info's included\Nin the deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was something that could{\i0}\N{\i1}carry a small woman inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't really say,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way he handled it{\i0}\N{\i1}sure didn't seem that way,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ni-lai-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel lethargic,\Nhave some ginseng hei-sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll last a week with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're tired,\Nhave sugarcane hei-sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate too much?\NThen have pineapple hei-sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme some lao-chu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. My apologies, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What, can't say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh- What? Ya pickin' a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the loot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I overhaul this whole craft,\NI'll have some change!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll go eat Peking Duck with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As they say, "Don't count\Nchickens before they hatch."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this one nailed shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, give it what you got.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So all three went down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hakim is around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, he doesn't even know how\Nmuch that thing is REALLY worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A pet shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A shady one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro, you can buy\Nanything here on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,From guns to human lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya wanna know,\Nshow me what ya got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The chain on this one is long.\NMust be the "Way of the Dragon" model.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can tell?\NThat's a rare one from the '30s!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is an antique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Try the store called Animal\NTreasure off of Caiphon Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll find something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll look... but I'll decide if I\Nwant to buy it from you after I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Run out of funds changing your\Nface around too much, Hakim?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are restless, changing\Nyour face around this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it. I don't want any\Nof this business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my babies are very sensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be some\Nsort of misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A Welsh Corgi.\NIt's cute, but it's everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a particularly rare species.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And how much is it worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With the suitcase, about this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,200K?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, 200, 200!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it, you take care\Nof it yourself. Like eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It IS a puppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you. Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the Peking Duck\Nhas been overcooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At least give me 300...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,280?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A no is a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,250!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO. I'll take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This again?\NWhat is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Catch my babies! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- There it is!\N- All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakim?!\NGod dammit, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Gangway!\N- What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bounty hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal rights syndicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story brings a tear to my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Risking your life on a dog\Nthat's only worth 200 woolongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want are the 8 million woolongs\Nhanging from YOUR neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuddup!\NI'm in a rotten mood right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.\NHere, lemme put on a collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog instead of a duck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about that!\NYou know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. This is a Welsh Corgi.\NA total mongrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally. Completely worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, this gives me a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And all this is\Nbecause of this mongrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog is worthless,\Nbut the OWNER is worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least you should get\Nto know this critter well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I hate kids and critters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nothing but trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I got something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's 4 o'clock now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that with Hakim? His ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We got no clues?\NWe have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If THAT falls into police hands,\Nwe're in deep shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All our work will be worthless if our\Nexperiments get revealed to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How much does he think we\Nput into that "data dog"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't YOU do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't your grandma teach you\Nto finish what you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She was dead before I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry to hear that.{\i0}\N{\i1}Anyway, we have the joker in our hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me code name "snoop."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's me.\NI had some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to postpone the meeting a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, it wasn't that big a deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible? Why? Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And THIS is our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something you\Nwant to know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My little Peeko can\Nanswer your questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something you\Nwant to know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See, little Peeko is telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you're looking\Nfor someone or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, where there's\Nthis dog, there's Hakim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, pooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We must resort to the dog whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But that'll cause a big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll draw attention to ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I said before that\Nhumans can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so farfetched...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this really attract?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's moving.\NSomething is now on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Babies, what's\Nwrong with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It got away, Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hakim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, the DOG!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:16:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's close, it's close!\NWhat you are looking for is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, right in\Nfront of your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, you need to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay when I am rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit, what the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Excuse me...\N- Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a dog, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike, he's headed for Interstate 6.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Great!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he thinks he can outrun me,{\i0}\N{\i1}he's welcome to try.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too hotheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What part of me is hotheaded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is payback from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...the HELL are you doin'?!\NThis guy is MINE!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,SHIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS is why I hate critters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}AMIGO!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How're all you 300,000 bounty hunters{\i0}\N{\i1}in the solar system doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for BIG SHOT, the show that{\i0}\N{\i1}brings you information about fugitives!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, you remember Abdul Hakim{\i0}\N{\i1}who chose a rather...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...flashy way of turning{\i0}\N{\i1}himself in last week?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah! Of course!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, he stole what's{\i0}\N{\i1}called a "data dog"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...created in an illegal{\i0}\N{\i1}experiment of some research firm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow! What's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure myself, but apparently,{\i0}\N{\i1}it's a very intelligent pooch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hear that it's{\i0}\N{\i1}priceless among collectors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a surprise!{\i0}\N{\i1}I wanna have a dog like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But they say it's still missing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder where it went?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really{\i0}\N{\i1}But now, a commercial!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there! When you're done cleaning,\Nfeed the komodo dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to work your ass off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't jump on there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said we should\Nthrow out mongrels like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the one\Nthat brought it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we have to do\Nsomething about the ticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna salt you\Nand eat you, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, it's time for us to go.{\i0}\N{\i1}See you next time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck!!{\i0}
