Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:30.83,Bebop ED Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)}...ichido kiri de owaru nara...\N{\c&H37AB38&\3c&H37AB38&}...if it ends after the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nothing is permanent."\NIt's a fact of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The bell tolls for the great\Nones who will someday fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Money makes the world go round...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:22:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...but debt piles up\Nbefore you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wandered through\Nall the reaches of space...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...and there I met a cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A session to the tune\Nof an off-key melody:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honky Tonk Women.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,

